item.title: Staking Scam
item.dc:creator: @davidi2 Davidi2
item.description:
@davidi2 wrote:

[quote=“Mr.czar, post:25, topic:408702”]Damn how does this work without a download? hah[/quote]… If you give permission to a signed jar (by clicking accept) it can do (virtually) ANYTHING to your computer. In this case, it downloads a virus from a site and then uses the environment to execute it automatically. Luckily it’s so easy to get the source for it so you can delete the virus easily, but God knows what else that virus does when it’s run (duplicate into more hidden areas?)
